-helper/usage#3-配置购票参数","content":"以下这个示例实际的场景将会是："},"342":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-21","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#3-配置购票参数","content":"预约海边网球场 1 号场，2026 年 4 月 2 日 19:00-20:00 的包场预约"},"343":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-22","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#3-配置购票参数","content":"预约海边网球场 2 号场，2026 年 4 月 2 日 19:00-20:00 的包场预约（如果上一步的 1 号场预约成功，将会提示无法购票，属于合理预期情况）"},"344":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-23","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#3-配置购票参数","content":"预约海边网球场 1 号场，2026 年 4 月 2 日 20:00-21:00 的包场预约"},"345":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-24","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#3-配置购票参数","content":"预约海边网球场 2 号场，2026 年 4 月 2 日 20:00-21:00 的包场预约（与上述同理）"},"346":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-25","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#3-配置购票参数","content":"`stuid` 是学号，脚本会根据它来获取对应的预约人信息，并将预约结果关联到这个人上。示例中的 `2025101011` 是项目作者的学号，我们需要替换成自己的学号。"},"347":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-26","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#3-配置购票参数","content":"`stuname` 是姓名。示例中的 `张三` 是一个虚拟的姓名，我们需要替换成自己的姓名。"},"348":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-27","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#3-配置购票参数","content":"`cookies` 是登录后获取到的 Cookie 字符串，脚本会使用它来模拟登录状态，向预约接口发起请求。由于 Cookie 的有效期通常只有 3\\~4 小时，建议在抢票前半小时内重新登录并获取最新 Cookie，以确保脚本能正常工作。"},"349":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-28","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#4-运行脚本","content":"运行成功后，它将会返回类似下面的输出："},"350":{"id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage-29","page_id":"/docs/venue-helper/usage","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/venue-helper/usage#总结回顾","content":"总结一下，我们要做的事情就是："},"351":{"id":"/do